```

**Grid (even simpler):**
```css
.parent {
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  height: 100vh;
}
```

**Just horizontal centering:**
```css
.child {
  margin: 0 auto;
  width: fit-content;  /* or a fixed width */
}
```

